of Quiet Mercy. <i>-What?</i>

477
00:24:20,611 --> 00:24:22,216
We all thought
you were at the Farm.

478
00:24:22,308 --> 00:24:24,476
Veronica,
there's not much time.

479
00:24:24,568 --> 00:24:27,329
You need to listen to me
very carefully.

480
00:24:27,421 --> 00:24:28,831
<i> Your text said</i>
<i>you had news.</i>

481
00:24:28,908 --> 00:24:32,176
